column12: How to use Warflash's public price sheets

column8: 1) a) Copy this sheet to another spreadsheet.
b) Rename the copied sheet to 'Prices' (after copying it will be called 'Copy of Prices').
2) Start looking up prices: See 'Look-up examples' tab at the bottom of the sheet.
Please use one of the lookup methods shown in the example tab. Direct references (e.g. =Prices!$B$2) will break over time.
Contact for questions about the price sheets and price fetching: warflash#1781.
Contact for questions about this guide: Summer#8727.
To view the ongoing discussion about market APIs, check out the dev-talk channel in the lifeskill Discord:
Feel free to delete the boxes above once you copied this sheet and got everything working.
